One can choose friends, but not family. Not all relatives wish us well. For example, most family members are capable of breaking your relationships. And do you know how? They choose to whom you can or can’t get married. READ: YOKI YOKI: VHUDI WOWS ON IDOLS! Those who’re not clever enough end up breaking up with their loved ones because of silly relatives who don’t approve of their partners. A few years ago a couple I knew called it quits because of this. To all those who’re facing such a challenge in relationships, do what you think is best for you. Never compromise your feelings – life is too short to please others. - Letter by Yvonne Petrus Gauteng